content:
You can export bot intent data using the Data Loader and the Intent Utterance object.

Einstein Bots is available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience. Setup for Einstein Bots is available in Lightning Experience.
Available in: Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions


USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED
To build and manage Einstein Bots:
Customize Application
OR
Modify Metadata
OR
Manage Bots

To manage intent sets and bot training:
Customize Application
OR
Modify Metadata
OR
Manage Bots
OR
Manage Bot Training Data

Log in to the Data Loader, click Export. Click Show all Salesforce Objects, select Intent Utterance (MLIntentUtterance) object. Choose a target for extraction, and then click Next.
Select fields to export: MLDomainName, MLIntentName, and Utterance. Click Finish.
title: Exporting Intent Data for Einstein Bots in Service Cloud
